The female condom is the most effective woman-controlled method for protecting against both pregnancy and STIs, including HIV.

Also, it is even more effective than the male condom in preventing STIs and HIV!', '0', 'en'), ('7822ec30-fccb-4922-979f-d5d98aa1db09', '8048de61-64b9-4c14-b4b7-134982d999e0', '869c23a2-1994-471d-8b98-e961fd6d9fef', 'How do you use the female condom?', 'The female condom is inserted into the vagina.

