It also protects from Sexually Transmitted Infections (STIs) including HIV. This is because these infections can be transmitted through semen, vaginal fluids or from skin to skin contact.', '0', 'en'), ('3fc26a59-c143-4fea-897e-a0d115eb3b7b', '8048de61-64b9-4c14-b4b7-134982d999e0', '869c23a2-1994-471d-8b98-e961fd6d9fef', 'How effective is the contraceptive injection?', 'Contraceptive injections are more than 99% effective for all users (perfect and typical).

