5. If the woman must be away from her baby for more than six hours at a time and cannot remove milk from her breasts during that time.', '0', 'en'), ('ffac75dc-b6c0-408c-a7d9-2327e4cbd67c', '8048de61-64b9-4c14-b4b7-134982d999e0', '869c23a2-1994-471d-8b98-e961fd6d9fef', 'How do you use exclusive breastfeeding?', 'To use breastfeeding to prevent pregnancy, you need to be sure of these 3 things:

