To make sure that you always have access to your account, go to your profile in the bottom left of the app and click ''Save account''. Make sure you have an internet connection when you do this.', '1', 'en'), ('23f2dae2-18ed-408f-94f5-d6d1b7e8e5e5', '1c94b11a-53aa-49b7-8835-26dd780c7eff', '08362b78-16da-4274-ba93-f6c14a3181cb', 'Do I lose my information if I update the app?', 'No! As long as you have saved your account, PeriodTracker will always have a record of you, and you can easily log in to the updated app and find your information.
 
