You can send us your topic and content suggestions through the ''Contact us'' button in ''Settings'' on your app.', '1', 'en'), ('5c9fcf9d-6fe1-47c4-bead-20d3b7be92bc', '1c94b11a-53aa-49b7-8835-26dd780c7eff', 'e06a70fa-084a-4157-9ef6-f431205fdff2', 'Can I still use PeriodTracker without regular internet access?', 'Yes!
 
